# ============================================================
# WHITELIST .gitignore — blocks everything by default.
# ONLY the items explicitly un-ignored below can be committed.
# ============================================================
# This is a PUBLIC repository. The ONLY permitted data file is:
#   docs/public_slim.csv — manually placed by Julia after ETL.
# It sits in docs/ so GitHub Pages serves it to the Shinylive
# app at runtime. The app is hard-coded to read from this one
# location only. No other data file can ever be committed here.
# No agent or script should ever write to this repo directly.
# ============================================================

# Block everything
*

# Allow this file
!.gitignore

# Allow the Shiny app source
!app.R

# Allow the Shinylive compiled output and its contents
!docs/
!docs/**

# Within docs/, block all data formats...
docs/*.parquet
docs/*.sav
docs/*.RData
docs/*.rds
docs/*.zip
docs/*.tar.gz
docs/*.csv

# ...except the one specific file Julia drags in
!docs/public_slim.csv
